PolishVocative
==============

Extends String class to provide vocative form of a name.
String#vocative translates only the first word of whole string
(usually a first name).


Example
=======

'KASIA KOWALSKA'.vocative # => Kasiu KOWALSKA
'Test'.vocative # => Teście
'Krzyś'.vocative # => Krzysiu


